ly and comfortably without risk of falling or colliding with people walls and other objects that hurt big environments – small footprint real estate is expensive and our customers tell us that efficient use of that real estate is critical the virtuix omni™ allows you to experience the largest virtual reality environments without leaving the omni’s compact frame multiplayer experiences are now possible in a small room  “try to resist throwing money at the screen” engadget  “if you really want that fullmotion experience what you’ll need is a gaming rig that lets you walk around as well enter the virtuix omni” the escapist  “ladies and gentlemen you’re looking at the future of gaming” road to vr  “impressive and probably the single best reason to ever play skyrim without fast travel” kotaku  “jawdropping virtual reality” pc gamer  “virtuix is finally bringing virtual reality gaming home” the examiner  this is going to be the “must have” video gaming system robert scoble  “hands down the most immersive gaming experience we’ve seen so far” business insider subscribe to our newsletter email address virtuix omni first of its kind active virtual reality motion platform virtuix omni active virtual reality for the commercial market contact us active virtual reality for the commercial market contact us walk in virtual reality whether you are creating a commercial entertainment experience a professional training environment or any other virtual reality application vr is best experienced with motion the virtuix omni™ is a firstofitskind active virtual reality platform that enables natural movement active vr where your movement in the virtual world is controlled by your physical actions like walking or running creates an unprecedented sense of immersion that cannot be experienced sitting down better yet … run in virtual reality we run in real life sometimes for entertainment sometimes for exercise and sometimes because it is our job why would you want to give that up in virtual r